text: Marie-Louise Castenskiold (born 10 November 1960) is a Danish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Denmark Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Holbæk Municipality
